ote":{"pid":"f1bcdc84017a6a789b2407a00218672b630395d6","tid":923670,"uid":152141,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"a23a3c31e7346fb93c51a6ea7ea40286d1ec5165","tid":923670,"uid":80308,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"507cc9e499ad99e25ac62a1374da2d92bfe32d1a","tid":923670,"uid":196924,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T12:52:50.000Z","msg":"除咗即場派彩不嬲都冇人要加p"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T13:15:05.000Z","msg":"咁即係1823 P牌行快線根本無撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T13:23:03.000Z","msg":"除非你行佢前面<br />\n你個後CAM 影到佢個靚仔樣清清楚楚<br />\n你咪叫警察對比個樣睇下有冇妨礙司法公正囉<br />\n前提係慈母肯彩你<br />\n阻住阿SIR收工燒春袋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T18:04:43.000Z","msg":"只要佢夠膽話人有相似 你都未必告得入"},{"pid":"e45ae929d3f0ba901a889779c513f8e49ff412d6","tid":923670,"uid":66242,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T18:24:27.000Z","msg":"已持有正式駕駛執照的人士，在駕駛車輛時掛上「P」字牌，是否違法？<br />\n最後更新日期： 2013年11月29日 <br />\n<br />\n已持有正式駕駛執照的人士，在駕駛車輛時掛上「P」字牌並不違法，但此舉可能令警方在執法時產生混亂，或令其他道路使用者有所誤會而造成不便。<br />\n<del></del><br />\n例如，當正式駕駛執照持有人駕駛掛上「P」字牌的車輛，在快速公路的最右線行駛，警方可能會截停有關車輛作進一步調查（因如果快速公路上設有3條或以上的行車線，掛上「P」字牌的車輛是不可在最右線行駛的）。因此，運輸署並不建議持有正式駕駛執照的人士在車輛上展示「P」字牌。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.1823.gov.hk/big5/FAQ/104004/index.shtm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.1823.gov.hk%2Fbig5%2FFAQ%2F104004%2Findex.shtm&d=c3cgBaPJNXi1TLONh%2BUXRwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=bf7d7b08\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.1823.gov.hk/big5/FAQ/104004/index.shtm</a>"},{"pid":"37750dea5cf829791b6243054dd6ba35739c28ce","tid":923670,"uid":21147,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T05:05:01.000Z","msg":"其實有啲假日司機 甩左p 但唔熟 都會掛p比提醒<br />\n人地小心啲 <br />\n<br />\n利伸：問過法律意見"},{"pid":"9724004d0efb2a38272843867ccd72e420fc1d0e","tid":923670,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T05:12:16.000Z","msg":"不嬲正式掛p行快線 只有警告 冇啦<br />\n個阿sir真係有做野嘢喎"},{"pid":"4c687f07c3f7c51060e366772b7356f4153cf302","tid":923670,"uid":94153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T05:33:31.000Z","msg":"唔係好明，掛 P 又冇犯法........<br />\n<br />\n可唔可以理解成，我都冇做錯，你憑咩警告我？<br />\n警告完再掛 P 又點？"},{"pid":"7682ac86eb4ac64b5ded59d15d1cddb5be57fb74","tid":923670,"uid":849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4c687f07c3f7c51060e366772b7356f4153cf302","tid":923670,"uid":94153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T05:33:31.000Z","msg":"唔係好明，掛 P 又冇犯法........<br />\n<br />\n可唔可以理解成，我都冇做錯，你憑咩警告我？<br />\n警告完再掛 P 又點？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T05:36:16.000Z","msg":"每個差佬經過截停你一次者<br />\n你唔覺得煩係可以繼續掛P<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9373108b413680b4c6f94944bcd207325f208bcf","tid":923670,"uid":69168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T05:39:53.000Z","msg":"1823只係轉介，咪又係差佬做嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}